[30;1m110 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m111 | [0m[35m        The NoneNode type is returned by the Graph, Edge and Node objects when[0m
[30;1m112 | [0m[35m        there is no match to a query. It has the same API as Node, but it always[0m
